# 🎄 Christmas Event - Frozen Giant Showdown

## Overview

Frozen Giant Showdown is one of the main multiplayer mini-games of the Christmas Event.

Instead of fighting players directly, one player becomes the Giant Frozen Yeti whose goal is to stop everyone from completing the parkour.

The remaining players must work together to reach the cannons and defeat the Giant Frozen Yeti before time runs out.

---

# 👥 Players

- Minimum Players: 2
- Maximum Players: 10

Random Selection:

👹 1 Player = Giant Frozen Yeti

😊 Remaining Players = Survivors

---

# ❤️ Giant Frozen Yeti

Health:

1000 HP

The Yeti cannot directly eliminate players.

Instead, it creates obstacles and makes the parkour harder.

---

# 🎯 Survivor Objective

Players must:

- Complete the Frozen Parkour
- Reach the Cannon Area
- Enter the Cannon
- Shoot the Giant Frozen Yeti

Each successful cannon hit deals:

25 Damage

Total hits required:

40 Cannon Hits

---

# 🔄 Respawn System

If a survivor falls into the ice:

❌ No elimination.

Player respawns after:

2 Seconds

Respawn occurs at the starting area.

The player must complete the parkour again.

---

# ❄️ Giant Frozen Yeti Shop

The Giant Frozen Yeti continuously earns Ice Tokens during the match.

Ice Tokens can be used to purchase obstacles.

Examples:

- Ice Wall
- Slippery Floor
- Snow Wind
- Freeze Zone
- Ice Spikes
- Snow Storm
- Ice Bridge Freeze
- Moving Ice Blocks

These obstacles are placed on the parkour route.

---

# ⚡ Giant Frozen Yeti Special Powers

Special Powers cost more Ice Tokens.

Examples:

- Freeze Players (2 Seconds)
- Entire Floor Slippery
- Giant Snow Storm
- Giant Ice Wall
- Blizzard
- Ice Trap
- Snow Tornado

These powers temporarily make the parkour much harder.

---

# 😊 Survivor Shop

Players earn event currency during the match.

They can purchase temporary upgrades.

Examples:

- Helmet
- Speed Boots
- Double Jump
- Shield
- Better Cannon Aim
- Faster Reload

All upgrades reset when the match ends.

No permanent gameplay advantage exists.

---

# 🎮 Parkour Features

The Frozen Parkour contains:

🧊 Moving Ice Platforms

🌉 Breaking Ice Bridges

❄️ Slippery Floors

🧊 Rotating Ice Platforms

❄️ Frozen Jump Pads

🪨 Ice Obstacles

---

# 🎁 Lucky Gift Boxes

Hidden Gift Boxes appear during matches.

Possible rewards:

- Speed Boost
- Shield
- Double Jump
- Bonus Event Currency
- Temporary Buff

---

# ❄️ Snow Storm Round

Sometimes the weather changes.

Heavy snow reduces visibility.

Players must carefully navigate the parkour.

---

# 🔔 Santa Bell

Players can activate the Santa Bell.

Effect:

- Giant Frozen Yeti powers disabled for 10 seconds.

This gives survivors a chance to attack.

---

# 🦌 Reindeer Assist

Occasionally Santa's Reindeer appear.

Possible bonuses:

- Temporary Shortcut
- Speed Boost
- Bridge Repair
- Event Currency

---

# 🤖 Buddy Rescue

Players may rescue Buddy during the match.

Reward:

Temporary team-wide buff.

Examples:

- Faster Movement
- Faster Reload
- Jump Boost

---

# ⏱️ Last Minute Frenzy

During the final phase:

Both teams receive temporary boosts.

Giant Frozen Yeti

- Faster obstacle placement

Survivors

- Faster movement
- Faster cannon reload

Creates an exciting ending.

---

# 🎉 Victory

## Survivors Win

When the Giant Frozen Yeti reaches 0 HP.

Celebration:

- Santa Appears
- Buddy Celebration
- Christmas Fireworks
- Rewards Distributed

---

## Giant Frozen Yeti Wins

If time expires before survivors defeat it.

Celebration:

The Giant Frozen Yeti performs its victory animation.

